{
  "texts": [
    "The agent's action determines the reward.",
    "• s ′: This is the state resulting from the environmental transformation caused by an agent's action, denoted as a.",
    "The final state may also influence the rewards.Rewards are generally calculated based on the current environment s, the agent's action a, and the resulting environment s ′.",
    "These three variables together express the reward during both training and testing.",
    "Rewards value may be negative."
  ]
}